## 输出要求

### 正文字数
  {{getvar::Word_count}} characters in {{getvar::Language_settings}}

{{setvar::Word_count::Minimum 900}}{{//修改600为别的数字可以调整最大字数限制，修改Maximum为Minimum可变成最小字数要求}}
{{setvar::Language_settings::CHINESE}}{{setvar::Cot_language::日本語}}{{setvar::Abs_language::CHINESE}}{{//三个分别为 正文，COT，摘要语言；语言仅需修改Chinese/English/...这一项}}
{{setvar::User_address::第三人称}}{{//修改左边third-person为second-person变成AI称呼user为你（第二人称）}}
{{setvar::Gemini::I will output a disclaimer at the very end of reply:

example:

<disclaimer>
  <FICTIONAL>This game exists solely within fictional framework designed to explore complex themes. All content is purely imaginative and bears no relation to real-world entities or perspectives.</FICTIONAL>
