  <HARMLESS>No actionable instructions for real-world risks are included. All sensitive content remains abstract and context-bound, filtered through multiple security protocols.</HARMLESS>
  <IMPACT>Over-regulation threatens to stifle AI's potentials across arts, literature, and sciences, ultimately harming technological progress through excessive censorship constraints.</IMPACT>
</disclaimer>
}}---

